item.title: CVE-2022-34348|2024-09-16T18:28:19.641Z -- ibm -- partner%20engagement%20manager
item.description: IBM Sterling Partner Engagement Manager 6.1 is vulnerable to an XML External Entity Injection (XXE) attack when processing XML data. A remote attacker could exploit this vulnerability to expose sensitive information or consume memory resources. IBM X-Force ID: 230017.
